    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>[I]n nomine Domini nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/115" key="#Princeps">Adelchis</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langubardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs><persName ref="#people/3603"
                            key="#Principissa">Adeltrude</persName> dilecte coniugi nostre, tibi
                            <persName ref="#people/113" key="#Prevosts">Crissi</persName> venerabili
                            <rs key="#Prevosts">prepositi</rs> et <rs key="#Medical_doctors"
                            >medici</rs>
                        <rs key="#fidelisOf">fidelis</rs> nostri <name ref="Ermenpertus"
                            >Ermepertus</name> et <name ref="Rainbertus">Ragempertus</name> seu
                            <name ref="Ermenaldus">Ermenandus</name> germani filii <name
                            ref="Maurus">Mauri</name> et <name ref="Leo">Leo</name> filio <name
                            ref="Causari">Causari</name>, <rs key="#Aldius">aldiones</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/84" key="#Monasteries"><rs
                                key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs> Sancti Benedicti</orgName>, qui
                        sunt habitatores in <placeName ref="#places/3451"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Privileges #Exemption"
                            >Cepalonis</placeName> et pertinunt ipsis ex monasterio cuiusdam <name
                            ref="Guacus marepahis">Guaconis</name>
                        <rs key="#Marepahis">marepahis</rs>, ut nullo in tempore dent <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Immunity"
                                ><rs key="#Census">pensionem</rs> nęque <rs key="#Angaria"
                                >angaria</rs> faciant neque <rs key="#Datium">hostes</rs></rs>, in
                        ea videlicet ratione ut ammodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum
                        preceptum predicta omnia que prelegitur fimiter habere et possidere valeatis
                        vos et rectores predicti monasterii, et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, id est
                        comitibus, gastaldis vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeatis aliquam
                        requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus firmiter possideatis. Quod vero
                        preceptum concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Abbots" ref="#people/3609">Thomas</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>. Actum <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Benevento</placeName> vicesimo tertio anno, mense
                        februario, nona indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
